נתונה פונקציה בשפת C:

```c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>

void process_input(char* input) {
    char buffer[64];
    strcpy(buffer, input);
    printf("Processed: %s\n", buffer);
}

int main() {
    char small_input[] = "Hello";
    char large_input[] = "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA"; // 100 'A's

    process_input(small_input);
    // Calling with large_input would lead to a vulnerability
    // process_input(large_input);

    return 0;
}
```

מהי פגיעות האבטחה העיקרית בדוגמת קוד זו?

